U.S. Faces Recession Risk, Bear Market May Worsen, DBS Says

-- B y   W e i y i   L i m
-- 
2011-09-26T02:17:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/u-s-faces-recession-risk-bear-market-may-worsen-dbs-says.html
The  U.S. economy  faces a “rapidly
rising risk of recession” and that may worsen the “bear
market” in equities, according to  DBS Group Holdings Ltd. (DBS)   China currently faces a “soft patch” and its economy
isn’t headed for a so-called hard landing, DBS said in
presentation materials given to reporters in  Singapore  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
